title: Jellyfish in Ocean
description: A vibrant jellyfish swimming gracefully in the ocean. The jellyfish has a golden-brown bell and long, flowing tentacles that trail behind it. The background is a deep blue, enhancing the colors of the jellyfish.

title: Mountain Stream
description: A picturesque scene of a flowing mountain stream cascading over rocks, surrounded by lush green grass and rugged terrain.

title: Lobster Underwater
description: A vibrant underwater scene featuring a lobster on the ocean floor. The lobster has a colorful shell with shades of orange and red, and long antennae extending from its head. The background includes coral and rocks, with a soft purple hue from the water, creating a serene marine environment.

title: Colorful Sea Anemone and Clownfish
description: A vibrant underwater scene featuring a sea anemone with long, flowing tentacles in shades of purple and yellow. A small clownfish swims nearby, showcasing its distinctive orange and black coloration. The background includes rocky formations and a blurred blue backdrop, creating a lively marine environment.

title: Fractal Design
description: A vibrant, intricate fractal design featuring a circular shape with a pink and purple color scheme. The design has a spiky, web-like texture radiating outward, set against a black background, creating a striking visual contrast.
